## Theme Registry

- Define themes in `lib/registry/themes.ts` as:
  - `{ id: string; name: string; css: string }`.
- The `css` field must be a precompiled global CSS string:
  - No `@tailwind` directives.
  - Safe to inject directly as `/globals.css` content in Sandpack.

## Component Registry

- Define components in `lib/registry/components.ts` with entries that include:
  - `id: string`
  - `displayName: string`
  - `category: string`
  - `description: string`
  - `sandpackTemplate: string` (usually `"react-ts"`)
  - `dependencies: Record<string, string>`
  - `examples: { id: string; name: string; code: string }[]`
- These registries must be static data used at build time:
  - No dynamic fetching or runtime mutation.

